00:07:31.270 --> 00:07:36.460
&gt;&gt; Todd Harvey: I took the
opportunity to look at some

00:07:36.460 --> 00:07:40.000
of the videos that you made
with the Lomax Project and I,

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:43.780
this is kind of a second phase
