00:12:57.160 --> 00:13:00.840
out some songbook sand
got online and we sort

00:13:00.840 --> 00:13:03.160
of collage together lyrics
from different places;

00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:05.880
oh like that verse, I
don't like that verse

00:13:05.880 --> 00:13:10.340
and then we just played it a
